vote.title: An ordinance granting a revocable license to Mark Cuban Cost Plus Drug Company, PBC for the use of approximately 29 square feet of land to install, maintain and utilize an electrical meter with a switch box on a portion of Taylor Street right-of-way, located near its intersection with Walton Street - Revenue: General Fund $1,000.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
